cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS

This paper is about reinforcement learning algorithms, which are commonly studied in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper deals with decision-making problems, which are often studied in the artificial intelligence community, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The paper also proposes a method for handling constraints, which is relevant to the fields of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper conducts extensive evaluations, which involves data analysis and experimentation, making cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) a possible category as well.
